      About this item

      • 【5G & 2.4G Dual Band】The latest 5G & 2.4G dual-band light bulb camera have stronger signal reception, higher stability, longer distance to use, no lag and smoother real-time video compared to traditional 2.4G single-band lightbulb security camera. Simply screw camera light bulbs outdoor into the equipped E27 bulb base (AC110/240V) and plug it into a power outlet, download the EseeCloud APP and simply connect bulb camera 360 degree wifi outdoor to your home wifi.
      • 【Two-Way Audio & Real-Time Alerts】Cameras for home security outside built-in microphone and speaker support two-way language real-time call, communicate with your family members or visitors without any obstacles, realize face-to-face communication. Light socket security camera can set up an audible alarm, when detecting moving objects home security cameras will emit a loud alarm sound and white light at the same time. Scaring away intruder and protecting the family safety.
      • 【Motion Detection & Body Detection Alarm】The PTZ camera light bulb is equipped with a highly sensitive motion sensor that supports horizontal rotation of 355 degree and vertical flip of 90 degree, realizing 360 degree blind spot-free super wide-range accurate detection and tracking of objects. If you turn on human body detection alarm in APP, once security camera outdoor detects human body movement, security camera will record the movement and notify you via APP,thus reducing false alarms.
      • 【2K HD Video & Color Night Vision Function】Outdoor cameras for home security supports 2K HD image, which is clearer than 1080P. The image is very clear in both day and night. Lightbulb camera supports color/infrared night vision, security cameras wireless outdoor can clearly monitor objects within 33 ft in low light environment, excellent night vision experience ensures your home safety 24/7.
      • 【Multi User Sharing & Smart Storage】Lightbulb camera 360 degree wifi outdoor supports multiple users to watch videos. You can share the device with your family and friends for simultaneous monitoring through the app. Camera bulb storage supports cloud storage (paid access required) and up to 128G micro SD card storage.Outdoor camera is Alexa compatible, easy to install and simple to operate.
      • Bulb camera size: 7.00 x 7.00 x 15.50 cm; Product Compatibility: Compatible with Eseecloud app and Alexa ;Product protection inside the package: 1* bulb camera, 1* manual, 1* light bulb camera socket.The clarity of the product will be affected at night and under extreme weather conditions.

      Motion sensor

      Light bulb camera has a built-in motion sensor for timely detection of moving objects, camera light bulbs outdoor lens allows you to view moving objects within a 355-degree pan & 90-degree tilt range. Lightbulb camera also sends real-time notifications to your cell phone when people or pets pass by.

      24/7 Playback

      Lightbulb security camera supports 24/7 video and stores it to the cloud or TF card (up to 128GB, not included in the product), you can watch the playback through the mobile app at any time, so you don't miss any wonderful moments at home.

      • Is there any difference between a regular 2.4G bulb camera and this 5G & 2.4GHz?

        Ordinary 2.4G bulb camera is easy to be interfered by the signal, 5G& 2.4GHz camera has a larger bandwidth, compared with 2.4GHZ signal is more stable, the picture quality is more clear and smooth.

      • Can APP connect multiple bulb cameras? I want to install one in my yard and indoor.

        Of course you can, multiple cameras can be added together within the app.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      • Sam's Mom
        5.0 out of 5 stars It's working for me
        Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
        Size: 1-PackColor: WhiteVerified Purchase
        This is my first experience with any kind of security device, so I have nothing to compare with, but I have to say, it has been reliable and efficient. It does not cut out on me, I am running it 24/7 with an SD card, and it has missed nothing. Day vision is great. I can see nearly everything on my block as I pan my camera. The sound is great too. A couple of days ago I could have (but didn't) eavesdropped on my postman as he was talking on a cell phone across the street. That's impressive. I like the way I can get playback on my smart phone--it's easy for me to check what's happened when I'm not home.
        Night vision had been great up to about 15 feet. I don't know if that is normal or not. I can see things that are close to my house very clearly, but it drops off quickly after that. I can see cars that pass in front of my home, but not enough to make much of them and people fade into darkness that pass on my sidewalk. But should anyone come close to the house, the view is great. It seems to follow people quite well most of the time. Though I live in a city, I have deer that come right to the porch at night, as well as feral cats, and I get good coverage of them. I had no idea a 12 point monster mule deer buck lived in my neighborhood but I have great night shots of him now.
        For the price especially, I am very pleased with this camera. I think I will look for another one that will give me better night distance and clarity, as I am specifically needing a camera for protection against a stalker, but I will keep this one running too. I've only had it a couple of weeks, but it has handled -20 temps at night and snow and has been a champ. And it was super simple to hook up and operate. If they are all like mine, I heartily recommend it.
        I am adding to my review. I've had this camera at least a month and a half and it is still working great, especially in minus degree temps. I have bought 3 other brands of cameras and returned them all for panning, connection and lag issues. I'm going to try a second one of this brand and see how it compares to the first. Hopefully as well - I will update when I do.
